  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Collection of thermal &quot;images&quot; of women with breast tumors in varying degrees of severity in
      order to evaluate and improve Real Imaging's device (&quot;RI3.0&quot;) capabilities , which will
      assist in early detection of breast cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
